snippet.title: IRAN RECRUITING TEENS ON PROMISE OF ISRAELI INVASION

localized.description:
Sub for more: http://nnn.is/the_new_media | Rowan Scarborough at the The Washington Times reports, Iran has begun to ask its teenage boys to volunteer to fight in Syria in a sign the hard-line Islamic regime’s military is suffering rising casualties in the five-year war and needs a morale boost, an opposition group says.

See the report here:
https://youtu.be/zgeGDR8DCzE

Read more:
http://m.washingtontimes.com/news/2016/apr/28/iran-touts-israel-invasion-to-recruit-teenage-boys/
